NAME
    Alien::OTR - Install and make available libotr v4 library

VERSION
    version 4.0.0.1

SYNOPSIS
        use Alien::OTR;

        my $cflags = Alien::OTR->cflags;
        my $libs = Alien::OTR->libs;

DESCRIPTION
    Alien::OTR installs the C library "libotr" version v4.0.0.

SEE ALSO
    *   <https://otr.cypherpunks.ca/>

AUTHOR
